 2023-11892023-12-01CIRNAC
ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectAmendment to the Anishinabek Nation Governance Agreement
PrecisOrder consenting to the amendment of the ANISHINABEK NATION GOVERNANCE AGREEMENT in order to enable the Anishinabek First Nations who have not yet joined the Governance Agreement to utilize community-based approval processes for ratification to be added as a party to the Governance Agreement post-effective date.
